# Barcode Scanner SDK Integration Guide

## Overview

The Barcode Scanner SDK provides a unified `BarcodeScanner` interface that
abstracts vendor-specific scanner SDKs behind a common API. Supported vendors:

{% for vendor in vendors %}
- **{{ vendor.name }}** ({{ vendor.sdk_name }}) — {{ vendor.description }}
{% endfor %}

## Quick Start

```python
from backend.barcode_scanner import create_scanner, ScannerConfig

config = ScannerConfig(
    vendor_id="{{ vendors[0].vendor_id }}",
    decode_mode="api",
    enabled_symbologies=["qr_code", "code_128", "ean_13"],
)
scanner = create_scanner("{{ vendors[0].vendor_id }}", config)
scanner.connect()
scanner.configure(config)
result = scanner.scan(frame_data)
print(f"Decoded: {result.symbology} -> {result.data}")
scanner.disconnect()
```

