## REST API

| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|--------|----------|-------------|
| GET | `/api/barcode/vendors` | List supported vendors |
| GET | `/api/barcode/symbologies` | List supported symbologies |
| GET | `/api/barcode/decode-modes` | List decode modes |
| POST | `/api/barcode/scan` | Decode a barcode frame |
| GET | `/api/barcode/frame-samples` | List pre-captured frame samples |
| POST | `/api/barcode/frame-samples/validate` | Validate a frame sample |
| GET | `/api/barcode/test-recipes` | List test recipes |
| POST | `/api/barcode/test-recipes/run` | Run a test recipe |
| POST | `/api/barcode/gate/validate` | Run full gate validation |
